BIEW is multiplatform portable viewer of binary files with built-in editor
in binary, hexadecimal and disassembler modes.  It uses native Intel syntax
for disassemble.  Highlight AVR/Java/Athlon64/Pentium 4/K7-Athlon
disassembler, Russian codepages converter, full preview of formats -- MZ, NE,
PE, NLM, COFF32, ELF partial -- a.out, LE, LX, PharLap; code navigator and
more over.

WWW: http://biew.sourceforge.net/
